  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6568.42 trading below the GEX flip at 6579, dealers are positioned to buy any dips toward the 6550 negative gamma wall while capping upside momentum into the massive 6580 positive gamma strike (+74.8B). The PIN regime with heavy positive gamma concentration between 6575-6585 creates a strong mean-reverting environment that should compress volatility and pull price back toward the 6580 anchor point. Watch for aggressive dealer selling if we push through 6580, but expect strong buying support on any move toward 6570 or lower as dealers hedge their short gamma exposure.",
